data.description: This 3/2 home sits in the heart of Myakka City on just shy of a 1/2 acre. This home is nestled in a lush and green environment offering a peaceful retreat with various fruit trees. Fruit trees galore surrounded with pineapples, avocados, cherry trees, ruby red grapefruit, lemon trees, lime trees, and grafted grape vines. The kitchen has been remodeled with beautiful grey cabinets and sleek granite countertops.  A large Bonus room 30x15 could be used for a Florida room, Game room, or an extra living room. The proximity to essential amenities and the local schools adds convenience. All (Elementary, Middle, and High) Schools zoned for this home currently hold the title of Manatee County A+ Schools. Enjoy the peace of Myakka City away from the hustle of town life.  Property is As-Is with the right to inspect.
